Class Potential

java.lang.Object
  gov.nasa.javaGenes.forceFields.Potential
Direct Known Subclasses:
StillingerWeber, Tersoff
public abstract class Potential
extends java.lang.Object

this classes used to find energy of a multibody system given a particular Chromosome for the potential parameters. Originally designed for molecular force fields.
